description:
WETSEAT  SEAT COVERS

All textiles used in the production of wetseat covers meet stringent Australian standards. All materials undergo testing with NATA Approved testing facilities. Some key testing features include:
  • Side Seat Airbag Testing at APV-Tech
  • Flame Retardant materials - An Aussie first!
  • Highly Water Resistant
  • UV Resistant
  • Mildew & Rot Resistant
  • Tear & Abrasion Resistant
  • High Tensile Strength
  • Antimicrobial
  • They are also designed to withstand harsh chemicals, constant rubbing and pilling.

If your vehicle is not listed please call us on 02 6699 2744
